{"id":"55395725","premium":false,"billing_type":{"id":"standard","name":"Стандарт"},"relations":[],"name":"Python Developer","insider_interview":null,"response_letter_required":false,"area":{"id":"160","name":"Алматы","url":"https://api.hh.ru/areas/160"},"salary":null,"type":{"id":"open","name":"Открытая"},"address":null,"allow_messages":true,"site":{"id":"hh","name":"hh.ru"},"experience":{"id":"between3And6","name":"От 3 до 6 лет"},"schedule":{"id":"fullDay","name":"Полный день"},"employment":{"id":"full","name":"Полная занятость"},"department":null,"contacts":null,"description":"<p><strong>Andersen Lab </strong>is a <strong>pre-IPO</strong> software development company providing a full cycle of services. For over 14 years, we have been helping enterprises and middle-sized firms worldwide transform their businesses by creating effective digital solutions using innovative technologies.</p> <p>Andersen Lab is a <strong>European IT company</strong> uniting over 3,100 top-class professionals: developers, architects, testers, analysts, and other specialists. Our employees are located all over the world, but we all are Andersen Family!</p> <p>Operating in the market since 2007, we have developed more than 1,000 outstanding projects for the financial sector, healthcare, logistics, travel and hospitality, telecom, the automotive industry, etc.</p> <p><strong>Among Andersen’s customers are Samsung, Johnson &amp; Johnson, Ryanair, Europcar, TUI, Verivox, Media Markt, Shypple, and other corporations. </strong>Thanks to the acquired expertise and reputation, we have a stable influx of high-tech projects from the above companies and new customers.</p> <p>We have been repeatedly recognized in various countries as the best IT employer.</p> <p>Andersen Lab offers a high salary, comfortable working conditions, a considerable social package, professional growth, and certification.</p> <p>Andersen Lab invites an experienced <strong>Python Developer</strong> to work with a British company.</p> <p><strong>The task</strong> is to develop a system for event booking.</p> <p><strong>The customer</strong> is a digital product development company founded in 2010. It is part of the AKQA Group network and works with such companies as Google, Mozilla, Royal Bank of Scotland, BBC, Amazon Alexa, and Cambridge Audio. The company is WPP&#39;s lead agency for Voice for its Global Center of Excellence.</p> <p><strong>Tech stack on the project: </strong>Python, Django, Firebase/AWS/Azure, PostgreSQL.</p> <p><strong>Must-haves:</strong></p> <ul> <li>Commercial experience in development using Python for 3+ years;</li> <li>Knowledge of and experience with Django framework;</li> <li>Knowledge of Firebase, AWS, or Azure;</li> <li>Strong knowledge of and experience with PostgreSQL;</li> <li>Experience with Node.js;</li> <li>Experience with large Digital projects in the fields of Media, Retail, FinTech, etc;</li> <li>Ability to write idiomatic, workable, and maintainable code;</li> <li>Level of English – Upper-Intermediate.</li> </ul> <p><strong>Reasons why this job would be interesting to you:</strong></p> <ul> <li>Andersen cooperates with such businesses as Samsung, Johnson &amp; Johnson, Ryanair, Europcar, TUI, Verivox, Media Markt, Shypple, etc. This project is just your beginning here – working with us means reliability and prospects;</li> <li>We have been strengthening our expertise since 2007. During this time, we have formed excellent teams with streamlined processes, where you can learn something new from your colleagues every day and enjoy your work;</li> <li>We welcome specialists from every part of the world;</li> <li>The salaries are pegged to the US dollar, and our employees are provided with a benefit package and an extensive set of bonuses;</li> <li>There are many different ways to grow and develop at our company. You can improve as a specialist or a manager, and all your activities will be decently rewarded;</li> <li>Our employees have access to Andersen Knowledge Base, where they can take courses on the art of negotiation, project management, Machine Learning and Data Analysis, DevOps practices, programming languages, cloud services, and more.</li> </ul> <p>We invite you to join our team!</p>","branded_description":"
